Note:
aott/analysis/dataflow/alias_analysis.runa
Alias Analysis Module for AOTT Memory Optimization

This module provides alias analysis for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Points-to analysis and pointer tracking
- May-alias and must-alias computation
- Field-sensitive alias analysis
- Context-sensitive aliasing
- Flow-sensitive alias tracking
- Heap abstraction and modeling
- Escape-based alias refinement
- Type-based alias analysis
- Andersen's and Steensgaard's algorithms
- Alias set construction
- Memory disambiguation
- Load-store dependency analysis
- Mod-ref analysis for functions
- Interprocedural alias propagation
- Alias analysis for optimization safety
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

